      "statement": "theorem procedural_AddAut_mulRight_symm_apply_df7baa1c1030 : ((\u2200 {R : Type _} [Semiring R] (u : R\u02e3) (x : R), (AddEquiv.symm (AddAut.mulRight u)) x = x * \u2191u\u207b\u00b9) \u2227\n    (\u2200 {R : Type _} [Ring R] {a b : R} [Invertible a] [Invertible b] [Invertible (a + b)] (h : \u215f(a + b) = \u215fa + \u215fb),\n      a * \u215fb * a = b * \u215fa * b)) \u2227\n  (\u2200 {R : Type _} {S : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring R] [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring S] (f : R \u2192+ S),\n    (\u2200 (x y : R), f (x * y) = f x * f y) \u2194 AddMonoidHom.mul.compr\u2082 f = (AddMonoidHom.mul.comp f).compl\u2082 f) := by\n  sorry",
